'''林錦公路'''（{{lang-en|Lam Kam Road}}）是來往[[香港|香港]][[大埔區|大埔區]][[林村|林村]]和[[元朗區|元朗區]][[錦田|錦田]]的公路，全長5.7[[公里|公里]]。公路由位於[[香港9號幹線|9號幹線]][[粉嶺公路|粉嶺公路]]及[[吐露港公路|吐露港公路]]交界的林錦公路交匯處始發，穿越[[大刀屻|大刀屻]]，在[[上村_(香港)|上村]]的[[錦田公路|錦田公路]]及[[荃錦公路|荃錦公路]]的迴旋處作結。林錦公路全程是一條雙線雙程不分隔的道路，為了在[[大刀屻|大刀屻]]至[[觀音山_(元朗區)|觀音山]]之間穿過，林錦公路於介乎荃錦公路至[[嘉道理農場暨植物園|嘉道理農場]]及介乎嘉道理農場至[[梧桐寨|梧桐寨]]兩段分別為斜度1:8及1:10的[[長命斜|長命斜]]，但東面的[[林村谷|林村谷]]一段則以平路為主。林錦公路乃早期[[元朗區|元朗]]至[[大埔區|大埔]]的主要通道，至1990年代新界環迴公路（現時之[[9號幹線|9號幹線]]）通車，此路的重要性已經大大降低，車流一般都是出入沿線鄉村及景點。現時林錦公路是[[香港的士#新界的士|新界的士]]可途經道路之一<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap374E?xpid=ID_1438403126425_001|title=第374E章《道路交通(車輛登記及領牌)規例》|website=電子版香港法例|date=2019-12-30|accessdate=2020-09-08|archive-date=2020-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718033126/https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap374E?xpid=ID_1438403126425_001|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而總長度超過11米的車輛都不可以進入林錦公路。

==歷史==
在1950年代，[[駐港英軍|駐港英軍]]為改善新界地區交通，先後興建林錦公路、[[粉錦公路|粉錦公路]]、[[屏廈路|后海灣路]]及[[荃錦公路|荃錦公路]]以利軍運<ref>{{cite news|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/c/portal/cover?c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqomgfZ0mNqalp&actual_q=%28+%28+allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29+OR+all_dc.title%3A%281949-06-18%29+OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281949-06-18%29+OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281949-06-18%29+OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281949-06-18%29+OR+fulltext%3A%281949-06-18%29+OR+all_dc.description%3A%281949-06-18%29+%29+%29&o=2&hsf=1949-06-18&sort_field=score&sort_order=desc|title=途徑測量工作完竣 林錦公路秋後興建|publisher=華僑日報|date=1949-06-18|language=zh-hk|accessdate=2020-09-08|archive-date=2020-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200908041556/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=1949-06-18&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqomgfZ0mNqalp&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=2&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%281949-06-18%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281949-06-18%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281949-06-18%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281949-06-18%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%281949-06-18%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%281949-06-18%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此路於1949年7月15日動工<ref>{{cite news|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/c/portal/cover?c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqopdvNmg2n4wP&actual_q=%28+%28+allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29+OR+all_dc.title%3A%281950-04-07%29+OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281950-04-07%29+OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281950-04-07%29+OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281950-04-07%29+OR+fulltext%3A%281950-04-07%29+OR+all_dc.description%3A%281950-04-07%29+%29+%29&o=7&hsf=1950-04-07&sort_field=score&sort_order=desc|title=橫貫新界東西两部 林錦公路下月開放 全程十二英里|publisher=華僑日報|date=1950-04-07|language=zh-hk|accessdate=2020-09-08|archive-date=2020-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200908041556/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=1950-04-07&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqopdvNmg2n4wP&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=7&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%281950-04-07%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281950-04-07%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281950-04-07%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281950-04-07%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%281950-04-07%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%281950-04-07%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在1950年7月28日通車<ref name=kung/>。林錦公路起初只准軍事車輛和緊急車輛使用，未有許可證之民用車輛一律不得進入<ref name=kung>{{cite news|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/c/portal/cover?c=QF757YsWv5%2Bh5KT9sfcXnL2%2BAkdSjXd0&actual_q=%28+%28+allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29+OR+all_dc.title%3A%281950-07-28%29+OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281950-07-28%29+OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281950-07-28%29+OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281950-07-28%29+OR+fulltext%3A%281950-07-28%29+OR+all_dc.description%3A%281950-07-28%29+%29+%29&o=8&hsf=1950-07-28&sort_field=score&sort_order=desc|title=林錦公路通車 只准軍警車輛通行|publisher=香港工商日報|date=1950-07-28|language=zh-hk|accessdate=2020-09-08|archive-date=2020-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200908041557/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=1950-07-28&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2Bh5KT9sfcXnL2%2BAkdSjXd0&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=8&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%281950-07-28%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281950-07-28%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281950-07-28%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281950-07-28%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%281950-07-28%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%281950-07-28%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc|dead-url=no}}</ref>，當局更不時派出[[皇家香港警察|皇家香港警察]]杜絕未有許可證之民用車輛駛入公路<ref>{{cite news|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/c/portal/cover?c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJDRgVj7nGbak&actual_q=%28+%28+allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29+OR+all_dc.title%3A%281950-11-05%29+OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281950-11-05%29+OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281950-11-05%29+OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281950-11-05%29+OR+fulltext%3A%281950-11-05%29+OR+all_dc.description%3A%281950-11-05%29+%29+%29&o=13&hsf=1950-11-05&sort_field=score&sort_order=desc|title=耗資兩百多萬林錦公路修成 普通車輛行駛要罰|publisher=大公報|date=1950-11-05|language=zh-hk|accessdate=2020-09-08|archive-date=2020-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200908041557/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=1950-11-05&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJDRgVj7nGbak&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=13&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%281950-11-05%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281950-11-05%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281950-11-05%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281950-11-05%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%281950-11-05%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%281950-11-05%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不过在公路沿線居民多番爭取下<ref>{{cite news|language=zh-hk|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/c/portal/cover?c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqopobSRfEc2KF&actual_q=%28+%28+allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29+OR+all_dc.title%3A%281951-02-05%29+OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281951-02-05%29+OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281951-02-05%29+OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281951-02-05%29+OR+fulltext%3A%281951-02-05%29+OR+all_dc.description%3A%281951-02-05%29+%29+%29&o=8&hsf=1951-02-05&sort_field=score&sort_order=desc|title=村民請准許通車林錦路|publisher=華僑日報|date=1951-02-05|accessdate=2020-09-08|archive-date=2020-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200908041626/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=1951-02-05&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqopobSRfEc2KF&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=8&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%281951-02-05%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281951-02-05%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281951-02-05%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281951-02-05%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%281951-02-05%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%281951-02-05%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[港英政府|港英政府]]在1952年3月9日決定全面开放林錦公路給[[公眾|公眾]]使用<ref>{{cite news|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/c/portal/cover?c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqopGjceiGFj5b&actual_q=%28+%28+allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29+OR+all_dc.title%3A%281952-03-09%29+OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281952-03-09%29+OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281952-03-09%29+OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281952-03-09%29+OR+fulltext%3A%281952-03-09%29+OR+all_dc.description%3A%281952-03-09%29+%29+%29&o=8&hsf=1952-03-09&sort_field=score&sort_order=desc|title=林錦公路今起開放 今後來往車輛不須如前領證|publisher=華僑日報|date=1952-03-09|language=zh-hk}}</ref>。公路开放為民用道路後一直並没有公共交通途經，直至1953年4月1日，[[九龍巴士64K線|九龍巴士64K線]]投入服務，至今仍為唯一途經全段林錦公路的巴士路線<ref>{{cite news|language=zh-hk|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/c/portal/cover?c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqognyEIC6Wgp2&actual_q=%28+%28+allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29+OR+all_dc.title%3A%281953-03-31%29+OR+all_dc.creator%3A%281953-03-31%29+OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%281953-03-31%29+OR+all_dc.subject%3A%281953-03-31%29+OR+fulltext%3A%281953-03-31%29+OR+all_dc.description%3A%281953-03-31%29+%29+%29&o=4&hsf=1953-03-31&sort_field=score&sort_order=desc|title=新界林錦公路四一行走巴士 縮減元朗至大埔路程一倍|publisher=華僑日報|date=1953-03-31|accessdate=2020-09-08|archive-date=2020-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200908041619/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=1953-03-31&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqognyEIC6Wgp2&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=4&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%281953-03-31%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%